Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.63,0:00:10.88,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:19.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:31.59,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:37.76,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King, Julius Novachrono, \Nprotected the kingdom's citizens
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:40.99,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,from an attack by the Eye of \Nthe Midnight Sun's leader, Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.99,0:00:44.77,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But as a result, he was gravely injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:46.94,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's going on here...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:49.23,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Vangeance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:52.16,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Good day to you, Yami Sukehiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.16,0:00:53.65,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I am Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.31,0:00:56.82,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Yami attacked Licht, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:00:58.12,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:00.37,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Cloaked...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:02.87,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dimension Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:05.33,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:07.63,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And Julius...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.94,0:01:11.80,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I leave the rest to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.62,0:01:14.42,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:20.89,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,This is goodbye for all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:24.98,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,You will serve as the foundation \Nof the resurrection.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.62,0:01:30.98,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Licht's true intentions were\N about to come to light!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.26,0:01:46.79,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(299,1)}Reincarnation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:13.63,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A four-leaf grimoire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:17.88,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Licht of sword magic was chosen \Nby a four-leaf grimoire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:20.51,main,kid,0000,0000,0000,,What's a four-leaf grimoire, Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:23.56,main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's a grimoire with good fortune in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:26.29,main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Only those it chooses can wield it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:33.77,sign_12339_133_Finnes_Calmreich,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(688,1)}Licht
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:32.93,top,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Licht, with the four-leaf grimoire...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.51,0:03:35.91,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,He's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.21,0:03:43.46,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Licht!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:48.49,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:51.83,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,You're so annoying,\N coming by every day. Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:53.17,top,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Shoo, shoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:56.59,sign_12339_133_Finnes_Calmreich,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(777,1)}Patry
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:56.59,top,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:58.22,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say, shrimp?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:01.86,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. He's not annoying, Raia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:05.71,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you came to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:07.35,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:11.10,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you think, Licht?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:12.23,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:16.56,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,About the rumors that the \Nhumans might attack us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:20.03,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I believe they're just rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:23.13,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,But I wouldn't say it's \Ncompletely impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:24.39,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.39,0:04:30.46,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are a wicked-hearted\Nrace that kills animals for sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:33.88,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Their magical powers are weak,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:36.47,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,but their increased numbers \Nhave made them overconfident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:38.75,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we elves have saved them
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:41.80,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,from countless natural disasters in the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:44.21,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they're just scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.21,0:04:45.05,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:47.31,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,They're just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:50.56,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,We're much alike, but they don't \Nknow that, so they fear us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:55.65,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,But we should be able to \Nunderstand each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:04:58.31,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,because we both receive grimoires.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:03.37,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:08.28,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,It's a tornado caused by \Nnatural mana running wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:10.29,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty big.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:12.78,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,It'll go away on its own if we ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:28.30,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Licht!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:32.26,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Someone else appeared \Nbehind the tornado?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:33.22,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.69,0:05:34.90,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Sword Magic:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:38.27,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Origin Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:40.69,main,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Light Magic:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:43.78,main,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Lamp of Avior!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:53.33,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Licht!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:56.98,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,He managed to destroy a tornado \Nthat big! He really is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:58.08,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:06:02.00,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that guy who just used\Nlight magic that seemed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:04.09,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,just as powerful as Licht's magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:07.25,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:09.09,main,Tetia,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:11.34,main,Tetia,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:16.44,main,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Tetia! Why did you leave the \Ncastle without permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:17.60,main,Tetia,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:20.17,main,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Your magical attribute is wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:23.50,main,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,How did you, of all people, \Nget caught up in a mana tornado?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:27.52,main,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for saving my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.52,0:06:28.87,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:44.88,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,He has a four-leaf grimoire, \Njust like Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:46.98,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,A human...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:59.15,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Licht sure has been hanging \Naround those two a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:03.65,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,He sure has. I guess he's happy \Nto have some human friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:07.37,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, those two are really decent people,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:10.62,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,and they seem to have the \Nsame thoughts as Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.62,0:07:11.70,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,The same thoughts?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:15.91,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,They were wondering if elves \Nand humans could get along, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:17.20,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:20.81,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Why must Licht keep hanging \Naround those humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:24.46,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,But Licht is never wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:26.94,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,And that human was also
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:31.30,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,selected by one of the four-leaf \Ngrimoires, just like Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:42.77,main,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,We can come to understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:45.86,main,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,You elves have truly amazing mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:49.71,main,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,By combining that with the magic-item \Ntechnology that we humans created,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:53.11,main,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,we can make this land \Nsafer and more prosperous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:55.85,main,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Let us live together, hand in hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:09.13,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You're with child?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:12.90,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,With you two as its parents,\NI'm sure it'll be a wonderful child!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:15.68,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats, Tetia... and Licht, too, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:19.43,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thanks, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.67,0:08:23.22,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,What? Something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:24.14,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:27.06,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you are still a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.37,0:08:31.63,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet! Stop treating me like a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:33.70,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah... Ooh, aren't you scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:35.70,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:42.20,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, Raia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:44.85,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Are you too lazy to even wake up nowadays?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:46.00,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,You're the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:47.77,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.30,0:08:53.09,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, Patry. Hogging the \Nspot next to Licht again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:56.90,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,After tomorrow's ceremony, \Nhe's going to belong to someone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:08:59.08,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,so you should probably cut the cord now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.08,0:09:02.35,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. I can do what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:03.99,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,What, you little brat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.99,0:09:08.52,main,Tetia,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. Even if I marry Licht, \Nhe still belongs to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:11.33,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,The human princess sure is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:14.28,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,That kindness is going to \Nbring you trouble someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:18.53,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,And pretty soon, there won't be \Nany room for you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:22.98,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Stop picking on him. Patry knows that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:26.79,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,So, Licht, how does it feel, knowing you're\N going to be a father in a few months?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:30.50,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel the mana blessing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:35.38,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very happy our child will come into \Nthis world welcomed by everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:39.54,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,This child is our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:42.35,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,It'll bridge the gap \Nbetween elves and humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.86,0:10:00.93,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:02.57,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you both years of happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:04.09,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,May the mana bless you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.87,main,Tetia,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:14.53,flashback,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of my little sister for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:17.97,flashbackitalics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I will protect her, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.67,0:10:21.78,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for being here today, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:23.74,main,Some,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.71,0:10:27.75,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's the day you get your grimoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:29.73,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Licht, you remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:32.06,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. How could I forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.35,0:10:37.52,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I'm excited to see which \Ngrimoire chooses you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:38.32,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:41.41,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Aw... I hope someday I'll also...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:44.62,main,Tetia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll meet \Nsomeone lovely soon, Fana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:46.16,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I sure hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:48.65,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you a lifetime of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:49.67,main,Tetia,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:52.67,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,If this guy ever cheats on you,\N let me know right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:54.45,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure to kick his ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:56.96,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on now, Raia...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:59.09,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:01.97,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Licht seems so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:05.93,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Licht always seemed happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:09.94,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bit jealous she's the one \Nwho made him happier, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.63,0:11:12.73,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of those two humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:14.61,flashback,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,We can come to understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:21.32,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we can come to understand \Nhumans someday, just like he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:23.28,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Licht seems to believe that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:29.71,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's possible... for elves \Nand humans to join hands someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:34.92,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:37.57,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The humans are attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:42.09,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,This way! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:44.83,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,I can't use any magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:48.54,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Our magic has been sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:51.48,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:00.61,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Run... quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:05.89,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You loathsome humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:11.16,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,This is light magic. That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:15.62,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,...dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:18.00,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:23.30,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:24.47,main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:27.43,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up! Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:32.93,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:34.14,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,This has to be a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:35.49,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:37.69,top,Some,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts! It burns!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:40.45,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you, how dare you, how dare you,\N how dare you, how dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:40.09,top,,0000,0000,0000,,They put up a barrier! We can't go—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:42.94,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you... How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:42.94,top,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.94,0:12:46.10,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you?! How dare you?! \NHow dare you?! How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:47.87,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you?! How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:49.83,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:26.25,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Licht...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:32.62,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Lich...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:41.33,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,...t...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:53.31,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Where... am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.19,0:13:56.06,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:59.14,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I die?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:02.86,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,These aren't... my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:09.45,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Licht?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:13.37,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? \NI somehow look like Licht!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:17.96,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Did my soul somehow end up in Licht?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:21.77,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,No... The feeling of this mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:24.06,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,This body... It's human!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:26.97,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,A human that looks like Licht?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:30.72,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... I'm sure that I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:36.41,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that Licht activated \Nwhen our magic was sealed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:38.83,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,It must've been forbidden magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:41.93,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning... a reincarnation spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:47.06,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:54.59,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell... I can feel them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:56.85,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Raia's soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:14:59.75,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,The souls of all the elves from the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:04.75,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Licht must have activated a reincarnation \Nspell in those last moments!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:08.76,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,In order to save us elves!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:16.52,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,But not everyone's been fully reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:17.77,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,It's just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:20.77,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Right... my grimoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:29.73,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,This grimoire chose the soul that \Ninhabits this body, so I can't use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:34.37,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I was chosen \Nor if this is sheer coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:38.06,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,But... I was the only one who was reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:40.62,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,And in Licht's form!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:43.88,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one who can save them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:46.86,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one who can!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:15:56.39,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:16:00.10,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,been chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:01.93,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I will become Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:05.53,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I have to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:09.11,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I will bring back all the elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:11.61,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,And this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:17.88,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,The humans betrayed someone precious \Nto me. They betrayed all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:18.87,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:22.63,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,This time, we'll destroy the humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:32.51,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Forbidden Magic: Evil Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:42.62,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I've added magic from the other \Nworld to your soul and assisted
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:47.74,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,your reincarnation in a human \Nwith a similar wavelength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:54.53,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Gathering the magical power I needed \Nto use this spell was no small task.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:58.53,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I'd appreciate it if you didn't \Ncause me any trouble, Raia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:01.09,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,You're Pat—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.09,0:17:07.79,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,However, bringing you back \Nis Licht's—no, my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.71,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Raia?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:13.99,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is, Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:18.34,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:19.50,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Raia...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:22.47,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,So you're finally awake. You overslept.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:28.23,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,All things considered, I wish \NI could've slept a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:31.93,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I was also able to resurrect these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:41.64,flashback,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Vetto... You're a kind soul \Nwho can talk to the animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:44.19,flashback,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, even now, you're being persecuted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:48.67,flashback,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Come live with us once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:53.56,flashback,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the one who should be in despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:54.78,flashback,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,It's the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:17:58.23,flashback,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Remember your true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:07.43,flashback,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,How unfortunate, my old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.09,0:18:09.81,flashback,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:13.46,flashback,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Humans still continue to harm other humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:16.32,flashback,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I shall destroy you all, \Nas you seem to desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:19.88,flashback,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,But I need your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:21.45,flashback,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.61,0:18:28.10,flashback,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Fana, not only do you look alike, \Nbut you both share the same name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:30.08,flashback,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,This cannot be a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:35.02,flashback,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't have to meet the same \Nsad ending in this lifetime, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:38.29,flashback,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Now... awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:49.35,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones I can resurrect \Nright now are these three.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:55.03,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,For a complete rebirth... In order \Nto resurrect everyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:58.45,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I will require a phenomenal \Namount of power and sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:05.06,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,We'll gather the magic stones \Nthat were once in our village,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:08.70,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,which have now been scattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:11.50,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,By using the humans, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:13.42,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a wonderful idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.38,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:16.00,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:18.27,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,We will get revenge against \Nthose loathsome humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:21.05,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I will give them endless despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:27.23,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Humans, you shall serve as the\Nfoundation of the resurrection.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:40.54,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Foundation of the resurrection? \NWhat the hell are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.54,0:19:43.66,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to awaken to an insane \Namount of magical power now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:47.53,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you actually tricked us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:50.91,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:54.82,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:20:02.38,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,When I gave you your new names and \Nwelcomed you as comrades, I marked you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:05.78,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,as sacrifices for this forbidden spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:13.10,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Forbidden spell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:15.34,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.34,0:20:19.45,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,You just randomly gave me that name!\N I've never used it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:22.24,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Rades Spirito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:24.66,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Master... Licht...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.71,0:20:28.20,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Were we not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:32.69,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,your precious comrades?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:35.79,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you truly were precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:37.73,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Then why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:39.30,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:45.30,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,You are sacrifices that will help \Nbring back my true comrades.
